{"tid":1083493,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後幾輪啦]#李佳芯 陳瀅 陳穎欣 杜小喬 陳法拉 苟芸慧 18-19 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽第29輪投選專區","createTime":"2019-03-29T15:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T17:59:15.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5626c9e3ab3b25907cc862ba6608e243c4e496c3","tid":1083493,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T15:59:25.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n陳瀅 : 麥明詩<br />\n鄧麗欣 : 苟芸慧<br />\n李靜儀@SG : 沈卓盈<br />\n馮盈盈 : 朱千雪<br />\n倪晨曦 : 陳法拉<br />\n文詠珊 : 李佳芯<br />\n陳嘉倩 : 陳穎欣@SG<br />\n謝安琪 : 林嘉欣<br />\n張曦雯 : 杜小喬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n超聯第二十八輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/diccKo6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdiccKo6.png&h=c2763ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7Z2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=89d072e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b930ef5de661b1ef71167755e31e3472e4d1e220","tid":1083493,"uid":92376,"like":145,"dislike":23,"score":122,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港超級女神聯賽第29輪</div>